high_descs: Turn to the right 90 degrees and walk over to the table.
Pick up the knife off of the table.
Turn around 180 degrees, then to the left 90 degrees and walk over to the sink.
Cut the onion in the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Take a slice of the onion out of the sink.
Turn to the right 90 degrees and walk over to the fridge, turning left 90 degrees to face it.
Open the door of the fridge, put the onion on a shelf, close the door, wait, open the door, remove the onion from the shelf, and close the door.
Turn to the left 90 degrees and walk over to the black table in the corner, turning 90 degrees to the right when your reach it.
Place the onion on top of the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Slice an onion with a knife to put it in the fridge followed by place it on a shelf.

high_descs: turn around and head over to the kitchen table on the left
grab a yellow knife off of the kitchen table
turn around, walk forwards a bit, then hand a left and walk over to the kitchen sink
slice an apple that's inside of the kitchen sink
place the yellow knife into the kitchen sink
grab a yellow apple slice out of the kitchen sink
turn to the right and walk over to the fridge on the left side of the room
place the apple slice in the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
turn left and walk over to the kitchen table at the end of the room, then face right to look at the black table at the end of the kitchen counters
place the yellow apple slice on top of the black table
anns.task_desc: place a cooled apple slice on top of the black table

high_descs: Turn right, go to the white table.
Take the knife from behind the cup on the white table.
Turn right, go to the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink basin into pieces.
Put the knife in the sink.
Take a piece of apple from the sink.
Turn left, go to the fridge on the left.
Put the apple in the top shelf of the bottom compartment of the fridge. Close and open the fridge door. Take the apple.
Turn left, go to the black stand next to the end of the sink counter.
Put the apple to the left of the bread on the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold piece of apple on a stand.
